3 years and 199 days. That's how long I've been on Instagram. When I first started, I was only interested in taking pictures of food and having fun with filters (I'm not even kidding. Scroll all the way down if you don't believe me. 🤣)
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
I then began to use the platform to promote my graduation recital and later my #JourneyToJuilliard. I've shown you my successes, my failures, my endless goofs, and profound frustrations. You guys have not only become  an integral part of my life, but also an indelible part of my core identity. ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
You see, without you, #PlayHomiePlay wouldn't exist. Without you, I wouldn't have had the chance to start my solo career. And without YOU, I wouldn't be where I am today. ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
I love you, Insta-fam. And I can't believe we just hit 100,000 followers. Rest assured, I will be doing a few giveaways in the near future to celebrate!! But for now, let me dedicate this piece of music to YOU. Thank you 🙏🏽🙏🏽

#JHMJams No. 137 || Despacito || Luis Fonsi & Daddy Yankee

#JHMJams #cover #series every #Tuesday's and #Friday's ↗️YouTube channel link in bio↗️

This one was a request from Mitch and Yejin! I guess they came across this tune and they’ve been grooving to it ever since haha Mitch also brought his new toy (an electric cello!!) so that was fun to play with. Hope you guys enjoy this rendition :) Full version on YouTube!
If you want to request songs we should cover in the future, there’s a monthly raffle for those who pledge on our JHMJams Patreon! You can find the link through my website in the bio and click ‘become a patron’ under the JHMJams tab.
-
the band: @yejin1608 @brandonilaw @mlyon3 @sumire_vln

Be sure to check out the JHMJams YouTube channel where you’ll find all of the previous jams we have made in full length! So if you’re craving more than the minute I can post on Instagram, go check out the whole thing on the channel!
